WEBVTT

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:30.616
Molim vas dignite ruku
ako ste ikad koristili Tinder

00:00:30.640 --> 00:00:32.256
da biste pronašli srodnu dušu.

00:00:32.280 --> 00:00:34.096
(Smijeh)

00:00:34.120 --> 00:00:37.496
Sad je zaista teško prebrojati jer to
pokazujete ovako.

00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:39.336
(Smijeh)

00:00:39.360 --> 00:00:42.136
To su sve primjeri kako tehnologija

00:00:42.160 --> 00:00:44.256
kreira nove obrasce

00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:50.296
koji nam omogućavaju da vjerujemo
nepoznatim ljudima, poduzećima i idejama.

00:00:50.320 --> 00:00:52.336
Ipak, istovremeno,

00:00:52.360 --> 00:00:53.896
povjerenje u institucije --

00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:56.856
banke, vlade, pa čak i crkve --

00:00:56.880 --> 00:00:58.256
opada.

00:00:58.280 --> 00:01:00.496
Što se zapravo događa,